Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:09.69,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Goooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.85,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.53,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:32.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's here. It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.13,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,, Are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:34.15,Line EN,,0,0,0,,All this. This is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.07,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Your dream's being fulfilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.07,Line EN,,0,0,0,,so just go back and leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.13,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And give Ide back, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:48.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibaji, were you listening to anything I taught in class?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.15,Line EN,,0,0,0,,"Give this back! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.71,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, give it back, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,because it's all about what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:56.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I want everything to be mine! Give it to me! More!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.94,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're like a child throwing a tantrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:01.68,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You think you get things by asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that if you're stomping, crying on the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,people will just drop things in your lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.21,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Then what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:10.02,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:15.11,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If you want something you don't have, then you must hand over what you do have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's called balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:19.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're making a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That isn't really appropriate for a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This is the last thing I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You just have to give your power to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.09,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Is that your final answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:32.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're responsible for your own responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:37.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Despite what you may think, I have learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.74,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's time to stop acting childish,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:44.06,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and that's why I'm just gonna take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:47.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You get a gold star!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.04,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's it. Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.95,Line EN,,0,0,0,,More! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hurry. We need to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Come on! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.34,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hibaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.11,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Come to me, Atomsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, this doesn't look so --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.05,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This is bad. We have to get out of here, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.89,Line EN,,0,0,0,,No! We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.71,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Gather round, men. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.81,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You young'uns are the ones who'll fuel space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I am never going to give up on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:11.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The champ's all right with a champ's destructive punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:20.04,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Aiko. You actually came back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:24.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's a bit too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:29.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Medical Mechanica is somehow planning on capturing that monster with his mochi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,but I don't think it's possible, and the potted plant is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:38.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Aiko, you were supposed to be our last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Who would have guessed that when it came time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to bring myself to use you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Take this and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:52.33,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.41,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Just take it! I know you've been saving this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.37,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You were planning to buy your freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:05.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You may as well take it. It's prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:08.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's been a knockout, and the 10 count has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Aiko, you're finally free. Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.07,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That potted plant... the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:53.02,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, God. That was just the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:56.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did my bat go? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You were doing so well just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.90,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Canti!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Is this a real date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.49,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'll call it a date if you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:13.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You want the pot, right? It's probably at Ide's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.96,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was something you ate that didn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Oh, Mori. -Oh, hi, Hibajiri's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.49,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Goodness. Is this your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.93,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Why, yes, ma'am. -No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.81,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Okay, Ide! Since you're not home, I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.18,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, by the way, what do you want from Ide?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:47.06,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, Hidomi hasn't come home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:49.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I was hoping she'd be here, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Why would you think she'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.38,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I was thinking they were dating, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Why does Ide get all the ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.26,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Oh, my. Is something wrong? -Aiko
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.83,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, Aiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:23.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Are you okay?  Say something! -Mommy？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.17,Line EN,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi? Hidomi, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.29,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweetie, you're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:33.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Mommy has been worried to death about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:33.95,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.74,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Have you? You don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.53,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You've stopped caring about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're quitting, closing the cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.96,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's the same with Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You don't care about him, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.26,Line EN,,0,0,0,,When your father took off for the plant,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.77,Line EN,,0,0,0,,he left the cafe in my care,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.03,Line EN,,0,0,0,,just like he left those headphones of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Sorry to tell you this, but it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.35,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Maybe, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:07.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the reason he came was to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.21,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I was foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.69,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I thought as long as I was at the cafe with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.53,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I would be able to wait for him, no matter how long it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:21.02,Line EN,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was for life to stay the same as it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:27.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,so the day that he came back would be the day I could finally become a real mother to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:31.26,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Until then, I'll do my best to be a good mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,High-strung, but it doesn't look it nya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.06,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If it's your bat you seek, it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.38,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I was wrong, though, unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:48.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You are bound to keep changing, Hidomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You were bound to fall in love, bound to become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.25,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's the reason why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Then let's do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.36,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.41,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Let's run it together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.74,Line EN,,0,0,0,,not because we're waiting for Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:04.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,but because it's where home is and where I want to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:09.24,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and the only thing that doesn't change is the fact that I can change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.46,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hidomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Wait for me. Okay, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:20.39,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Come back soon, Hidomi. We have a cafe to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:47.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ms. Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:51.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Did you calm down? Want some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.90,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This power, I'm gonna use it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.67,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.84,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Who would've guessed the kid would be all selfless and noble?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here, and I'm taking Ide back with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.64,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That sounds good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:11.16,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That said, not thinking about what could happen next is what makes you a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:15.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If you take that off, Hibaji, you won't be able to stay human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Guess you're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:22.07,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Do you still want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.16,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Canti?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.34,Line EN,,0,0,0,,So, shall we make our way out of here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:21.54,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I was wondering the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:24.41,Line EN,,0,0,0,,A lot of crap got sucked in, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:27.53,Line EN,,0,0,0,,so we've just got to make sure to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:44.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's too hard! I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:53.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What an odd girl she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:13:59.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I prefer unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.77,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's what you call unique?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:29.48,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:45.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There it is. I can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's what happens in the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.99,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:08.72,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Canti!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The hell? Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's Atomsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.83,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Come on, Atomsk. Come back! -Come on! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I see. I have to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:51.09,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If you want it, then take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.89,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'll take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:16.06,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, go away, Hibaji! Stop cock-blocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.30,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.28,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.85,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.13,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Okay. You better not run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You became mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.34,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Didn't you, Atomsk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.90,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.97,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Why the hell won't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.58,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I've been chasing you for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep refusing to be mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You are mine! I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're mine! You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:33.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Why won't you...look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:37.17,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Can't you see my body is overflowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.97,Line EN,,0,0,0,,When you were a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,did you ever try drawing a picture of going to see fireworks with your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.37,Line EN,,0,0,0,,only to fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.81,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.84,Line EN,,0,0,0,, You try to draw the countless   specks of light that you saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,, but the only way to recreate the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,, is to color everything in with a black pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.21,Line EN,,0,0,0,,They were lighting up that dark sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and they were so colorful and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:23.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,All beautiful things eventually fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I thought, this time for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:42.99,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that I was gonna get what I was fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,So an all-out attack didn't work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.28,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Wait. What was the reason for doing all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,No reason for any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:14.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That thing probably didn't come for a specific reason, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, my tummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.85,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If at first you don't succeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.28,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You haven't learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:59.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The fact that you can't catch it is what makes you want to chase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.77,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The fact that you can't reach it is what makes you want to chase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ms. Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:13.02,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well -- Well, you and I know we experienced many different things on many different occasions,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.58,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and I appreciate your feelings. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, but I can't --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:23.42,Line EN,,0,0,0,,While I like you, I confess, I don't feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.05,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ms. Haruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, man. I'm so wounded by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I can't face you. I must run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.98,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want 'cause I'll be doing the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:51.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Haruko out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.69,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Chief? -Oh, how cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:21.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You have tiny eyebrows just like your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:27.31,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, don't look! It's so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:39.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:41.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:45.06,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and that's probably not the best way to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,but you know what? It probably doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.72,0:00:09.69,Line CN,,0,0,0,,上啊啊啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.85,Line CN,,0,0,0,,見鬼
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.53,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.58,0:00:32.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,它來了 它來了！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.13,Line CN,,0,0,0,,它終於來了！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你現在滿意了？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.06,0:01:34.15,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這一切 這就是你想要的 對嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.07,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你的夢想實現了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.07,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那就回去 不要再來糾纏我們！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.13,Line CN,,0,0,0,,還有 求求你 把井出還給我
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.28,0:01:48.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,雲雀弄 你在學校上課都不聽講的嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.15,Line CN,,0,0,0,,「把這個還給我！把那個還給我！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.71,Line CN,,0,0,0,,求求你 還給我
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,因為這一切只與我想要什麼有關
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.45,0:01:56.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我什麼都想要 給我！更多！」
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.94,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你就像個耍脾氣的小鬼
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.94,0:02:01.68,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你覺得開口索求就能如願
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,跺著腳 在地上哭
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,別人就會把東西放在你面前？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.21,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那我該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.95,0:02:10.02,Line CN,,0,0,0,,交出來
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.65,0:02:15.11,Line CN,,0,0,0,,想要什麼東西 就要拿你擁有的東西來換
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這就叫平衡{等價交換}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.36,0:02:19.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你想做交易？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,作為老師這不合適吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這是我教你的最後一件事
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你只要把力量給我就可以了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.09,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這就是你的最終答案嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.09,0:02:32.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼回應是你的自由
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.72,0:02:37.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也許與你所想不同 但我確實明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.74,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是時候停止幼稚的行為了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.74,0:02:44.06,Line CN,,0,0,0,,因此我要親手奪回來
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.74,0:02:47.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,獎勵你一朵小紅花
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.04,Line CN,,0,0,0,,就是這樣 把它給我！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.95,Line CN,,0,0,0,,更多！更多！
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,快點！我們要撤離了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,來啊！正面上我啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.34,Line CN,,0,0,0,,謝啦 雲雀弄
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.11,Line CN,,0,0,0,,終於到時候了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,到我這裡來 Atomsk
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,蛤？等等等等等！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好大！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,看起來不——
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,救 救命！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不妙 隊長 我們撤離吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.89,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.71,Line CN,,0,0,0,,集合  聽我說
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.81,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你們這些年輕人將是宇宙的燃料
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我絕不會放棄你們！
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.45,0:05:11.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,受了冠軍的重擊 但是冠軍沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.06,0:05:20.04,Line CN,,0,0,0,,愛子 你居然回來找我了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.39,0:05:24.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,可惜 已經太晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.41,0:05:29.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,Medical Mechanica 似乎想要用麻薯抓住那個怪物
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是我覺得這是不可能的 還有那個花盆也不見了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.97,0:05:38.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,愛子 你本應該是我們最後的希望
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,沒想到 到了應該使用你的時候
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我卻不忍心下手了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,拿好這個 走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.02,0:05:52.33,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.41,Line CN,,0,0,0,,拿走！我知道你一直在存錢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.37,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你想要贖買自己的自由
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.20,0:06:05.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,拿走吧 這是勝者的獎金
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.23,0:06:08.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,已經 KO 了 讀秒已經開始了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,愛子 你自由了 走吧！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.07,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那個花盆… 觸發裝置…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.18,0:06:53.02,Line CN,,0,0,0,,天啊 真是糟透了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.76,0:06:56.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我的球棒呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？剛剛不還好好的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.90,Line CN,,0,0,0,,Canti
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這算真正的約會嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.49,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你閉嘴的話就算
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.77,0:07:13.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你要花盆的話 應該是在井出家裡
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.96,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也許你吃了不該吃的東西
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-啊 森君 -你好 雲雀弄夫人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.49,Line CN,,0,0,0,,啊啦 這是女朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.93,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-當然啦！-才不是
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.81,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出 既然你不在家 我就進來了！
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.18,Line CN,,0,0,0,,對了 您過來是為什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.18,0:07:47.06,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美還沒有回家
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.06,0:07:49.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我想她會不會在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,為什麼您覺得她會在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.38,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我以為他們在交往
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,為什麼井出的桃花運這麼好
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這麼快
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.26,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-哎呀 怎麼了？-愛子？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.83,Line CN,,0,0,0,,天啊！愛子！
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.22,0:08:23.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-你沒事吧？說話呀！-媽媽？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.17,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美？ 酷美 是你嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.29,Line CN,,0,0,0,,親愛的 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.29,0:08:33.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,媽媽我好擔心
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.31,0:08:33.95,Line CN,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.74,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你才不在乎呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.53,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你已經不在乎我了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你放棄了 你關掉了咖啡店
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.96,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你和父親一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你也不在乎他
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.26,Line CN,,0,0,0,,在你父親去工廠之前
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.77,Line CN,,0,0,0,,他把咖啡店留給我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.03,Line CN,,0,0,0,,就像他把耳機留給你一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 但是不在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.35,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那可麻煩了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,或許還有救
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.72,0:09:07.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也許他回來的理由就是想取回它
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.21,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我真傻
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.69,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我以為只要我和你在一起經營咖啡店
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.53,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我就可以一直等下去 等他回來
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.45,0:09:21.02,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我想要的只是生活和以前一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.02,0:09:27.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,當他回來的時候 我就可以成為你真正的母親
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.79,0:09:31.26,Line CN,,0,0,0,,在那之前 我會努力做一個好媽媽
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,弦上的很緊{不確定} 但是看起來不是喵
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.06,Line CN,,0,0,0,,如果你想要你的球棒 它在那裡
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.38,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是我錯了 忘記了現實
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.76,0:09:48.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美 你注定是要改變的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你注定會喜歡上某人 注定要長大成人
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.25,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這就是為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那麼我們一起吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.36,Line CN,,0,0,0,,咖啡店
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.41,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我們一起開吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.74,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不是為了等父親回來
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.74,0:10:04.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,而是因為那是我們的家 是我想要生活的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.12,0:10:09.24,Line CN,,0,0,0,,如果說有什麼不會改變 那就是我可以改變自己
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.46,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,等我回來好嗎？媽媽
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,早點回來
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.32,0:10:20.39,Line CN,,0,0,0,,早點回家 酷美 咖啡店還等著開門呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,等我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.24,0:10:47.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,晴子老師
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.87,0:10:51.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你冷靜下來了？要喝茶嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.90,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這份力量 我要為自己使用
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.67,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不錯哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.84,Line CN,,0,0,0,,誰說這小鬼會高尚無私的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我要從這裡逃出去 而且我要把井出也帶回去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.64,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這也挺好嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.89,0:11:11.16,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不過 就因為你做事不計後果 才只能做一個小鬼
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.16,0:11:15.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,把耳機摘下來的話 你就無法維持人類的形態了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你會是孤獨一人
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.86,0:11:22.07,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你確定要這麼做喵？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.16,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,Canti？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.34,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我們從這裡逃出去吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.34,0:13:21.54,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我也這麼想
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.54,0:13:24.41,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好多垃圾都被吸進來了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.41,0:13:27.53,Line CN,,0,0,0,,所以一定要小心
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.54,0:13:44.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,太難了 我踩不動了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.27,0:13:53.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,真是個古怪的小姑娘
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.08,0:13:59.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是獨特！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.77,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這是你說的獨特？！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.77,0:14:29.48,Line CN,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,別擋路！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.71,0:14:45.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那裡 能成功的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我應該能出去的!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,電影裡都是那麼演的!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.99,Line CN,,0,0,0,,還有一處
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.76,0:15:08.72,Line CN,,0,0,0,,Canti!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼？到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是 Atomsk
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.83,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出！
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-喂 Atomsk 回來！-出來啊 井出！
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好吧 我要上了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.19,0:15:51.09,Line CN,,0,0,0,,想要的話就去拿！
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.89,Line CN,,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.57,0:16:16.06,Line CN,,0,0,0,,走開 雲雀弄！別來掃興！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.38,Line CN,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.28,Line CN,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.82,0:17:33.85,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.13,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好吧 你可不要跑
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你成為了我的所有物
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.34,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不是嗎 Atomsk？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.90,Line CN,,0,0,0,,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.97,Line CN,,0,0,0,,到底為什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那麼久…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.58,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我追逐了你那麼久
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,為什麼你不願意成為我的所有物？！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你是我的！我告訴你！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你是我的！你是我的！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你是！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.84,0:18:33.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你為什麼…不願意看我？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.69,0:18:37.17,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我的身體都溢出了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.97,Line CN,,0,0,0,,當你還小的時候…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你有沒有試著畫過自己和家人一起去看煙火
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.37,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但卻畫不出來？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.81,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你醒了！
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.84,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你想要畫出你看見的無數光點
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是重現夜空的唯一方法
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,就是用黑色鉛筆把一切都塗上顏色
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.21,Line CN,,0,0,0,,它們照亮了夜空
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,絢爛奪目
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.92,0:19:23.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,所有美麗的事物最終都將消逝
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我以為這次一定可以的…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.78,0:19:42.99,Line CN,,0,0,0,,一定可以得到我想要的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,所以火力齊發也沒有奏效啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你可以回家了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.28,Line CN,,0,0,0,,所以這一切到底是為了什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,沒什麼理由
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.97,0:20:14.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那傢伙過來大概也沒什麼特別的理由
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我的肚子好痛！
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.85,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你現在打算做什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,失敗是…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.28,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你真是不長教訓
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,因為我是個大人
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.37,0:20:59.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,追尋只是因為無法抓獲
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.77,Line CN,,0,0,0,,追尋只是因為觸碰不到
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,晴子老師
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎啦？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.10,0:21:13.02,Line CN,,0,0,0,,呃 你和我發生了很多事情
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.58,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我很感激 真的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,對不起 但是我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.19,0:21:23.42,Line CN,,0,0,0,,雖然我喜歡你 但是這是不一樣的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,晴子老師？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我好受傷
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我沒辦法面對你了 我得走了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.98,Line CN,,0,0,0,,想做就做吧 因為我也會做同樣的事
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.98,0:21:51.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,晴子退場！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好久不見 孩子們
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.69,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-長官？-真可愛
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.69,0:22:21.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你跟你父親一樣 眉毛都那麼小
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.16,0:22:27.31,Line CN,,0,0,0,,別看！好害羞！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.79,0:22:39.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我對自己毫無期待
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.95,0:22:41.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我什麼事情都不想做
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.31,0:22:45.06,Line CN,,0,0,0,,這也許不是什麼好事
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是 這也許沒什麼
